trans-unit.source: Represents an <xref:System.Int32> property (and the value of the property) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref:System.Int32>egenskapen (og verdien for egenskapen) av en utskrift maskinvare eller programvare systemkomponent.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> klasse for den angitte egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` bør fullt nøyaktig lik navnet på en bestemt <xref:System.Int32>-egenskapen for et trykt systemobjekt, inkludert små og.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>for en <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objektet må være stavet "AveragePagesPerMinute", ikke "AveragePPM" eller "AveragePagesperMinute".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.Int32> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på den <xref:System.Int32>egenskapen som det <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representerer.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> class for the specified attribute and gives it the specified value.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> klasse for det angitte attributtet og gir den angitte verdien.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` bør fullt nøyaktig lik navnet på en bestemt <xref:System.Int32>-egenskapen for et trykt systemobjekt, inkludert små og.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>for en <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objektet må være stavet "AveragePagesPerMinute", ikke "AveragePPM" eller "AveragePagesperMinute".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.Int32> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på den <xref:System.Int32>egenskapen som det <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representerer.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: The value of <xref:System.Object> the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir verdien for egenskapen som det <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representerer.

trans-unit.source: The property cannot be set to the value that the calling code provides.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen kan ikke angis til verdien kall koden gir.
